						<summary>

						<p>Kōdaṇḍarāmaśvāmin temple, south base.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">••• •••• Vṛisha, Paṅguṉi 4.</hi></p>						

						<p>In late characters.</p>						

						<p>Records the endowment of 30 <hi rend="italic">paṇam</hi> for the celebration of the festival <hi rend="italic">poli-veṭṭi-chiṛappu (puli-vēṭṭai-chchiṟappu</hi>-tiger hunt ?) in the month of <hi rend="italic">āvaṇi</hi> as Appayaṅgār-tiruva-tiru-chiṟappu with the interest <hi rend="italic">(vaḍḍi)</hi> (to be contributed, by Aiparāma-chakkiṟavatti Rāyayaṅgār for God Reghunāthapperumāḷ, by Āchchaman (wife ? of) Pattaṅgi Āppaiyaṅgār.</p>						

						</summary>
